          "content": {
            "size": 1756,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"_id\":\"699967a22ed6f8ab19f76552\",\"firstRemainder\":\"Dear ${studentName},\\n\\nI hope this message finds you well. This is a gentle reminder that your payment is due on ${installment_date}th of this month. To avoid any late fees or disruptions, please ensure that the payment is made by the due date. Please note that after the due date, a late fee of Rs. 100 per day will be charged until the payment is received.\\n\\nIf you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out.\\n\\nThank you for your prompt attention to this matter.\\n\\nInstallment Date : ${DueDates}\\nLate Fees : ${LateFees}\\nInstallment Amount : Rs ${InstallmentAmount}/-\\n\\nBest regards,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName.companyName}\\n${companyName.companyAddress}\\nPhone: +91 ${companyName.companyPhone}\",\"thirdRemainder\":\"Dear ${studentName},\\n\\nI hope this message finds you well. This is a gentle reminder that your payment is due on ${installment_date}th of this month. To avoid any late fees or disruptions, please ensure that the payment is made by the due date. Please note that after the due date, a late fee of Rs. 100 per day will be charged until the payment is received.\\n\\nIf you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out.\\n\\nThank you for your prompt attention to this matter.\\n\\nInstallment Date : ${DueDates}\\nLate Fees : ${LateFees}\\nInstallment Amount : Rs ${InstallmentAmount}/-\\n\\nBest regards,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName.companyName}\\n${companyName.companyAddress}\\nPhone: +91 ${companyName.companyPhone}\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-02-21T08:06:58.501Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-02-21T08:06:58.501Z\",\"__v\":0}]"
          },
