          "content": {
            "size": 7237,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"_id\":\"69b13f783b63287214f4cb43\",\"customTemplate\":\"Dear ${studentInfo.name},\\nCare Of: ${studentInfo.father_name},\\nMobile: ${studentInfo.mobile_number},\\nAddress: ${studentInfo.present_address},\\nCity: ${studentInfo.city}\\n\\nWe have previously communicated with you regarding the outstanding fees and continuous absentism for the ${courseName.courseName} at ${companyName.companyName}. Despite our previous notices, the payment remains unsettled.\\n\\nThis letter serves as your final reminder and an opportunity to rectify the situation before further action is taken. The outstanding balance for your ${courseName.courseName} is Rs ${studentInfo.remainingCourseFees}/-.\\n\\nWe understand that circumstances may have led to the delay in payment. However, it is crucial to resolve this matter promptly, as failure to do so will result in the following consequences:\\n\\n1. Certificate Issuance: \\nIf the outstanding fees are not cleared by the 20th of this month, we will be unable to issue your ${courseName.courseName} course completion certificate.\\n2. Admission Status: \\nIf the fees remain unpaid after this deadline, your admission will be considered cancelled.\\n\\nTo settle your outstanding fees, you can use the following payment methods:\\n\\n1. Online Payment: \\nYou can pay using Google Pay, Phone Pay, Paytm, UPI, Cash, Cheque, Credit Card, or Bharat Pay.\\n2. In-Person Payment: \\nYou may also visit our accounts department in institute during business hours to make the payment in person. \\n\\nPlease bring this letter with you for reference. We urge you to act swiftly to resolve this matter.\\n\\nSincerely,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName.companyName}\\n${companyName.companyAddress}\\nPhone: +91 ${companyName.companyPhone}\",\"cancellationTemplate\":\"Dear ${studentInfo.name},\\nCare Of: ${studentInfo.father_name},\\nMobile: ${studentInfo.mobile_number},\\nCourse Name : ${courseName.courseName}\\nStudent Roll Number : ${studentInfo.rollNumber}\\nStudent Remaining Course Fees : ${studentInfo.remainingCourseFees}\\n\\nSubject: Final Confirmation of Admission Cancellation\\n\\nDear ${studentInfo.name},\\n\\nWe hope this email finds you well.\\n\\nThis is to inform you that, as per our previous communications and the terms of enrollment at ${companyName.companyName}, your admission has been canceled due to the following reasons:\\n\\n<b>Non-submission of Pending Fees:</b> Despite multiple reminders, the pending fees for your course remain unpaid.\\n<b>Prolonged Absenteeism:</b> There has been an extended period of absence from the training sessions without any prior notice or valid justification.\\nThe decision to cancel your admission has been made after thorough consideration and adherence to our policies.\\n\\nPlease note that this is the final confirmation of your admission cancellation. If you have any belongings, course materials, or pending matters to resolve, you are requested to contact the administration office at the earliest convenience.\\n\\nShould you require any further clarification, feel free to reach out to us at +91 ${companyName.companyPhone}.\\n\\nWe wish you the best in your future endeavors. Let me know if you'd like to make any adjustments!\\n\\nWarm regards,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName.companyName}\\n${companyName.companyAddress}\\n${companyName.companyWebsite}\\n\\n\",\"dynamicTemplate\":\"To,\\nAll Students\\n${companyName}\\nSubject: Important Notice for All Students\\n\\nDear Students,\\n\\nThis is to inform you that all fee payments must be deposited directly into the official institute account (mentioned below). The institute will not be responsible for any transactions made to personal accounts under any circumstances.\\n\\nAcademy Bank Details:\\nAc. Name: Visual Media Academy\\nAccount: 7808540007\\nIFSC: IDIB000C073\\nBank: Indian Bank\\n\\nPlease ensure that all fee deposits are made only through the authorized channels as communicated by the administration. Any payment made outside of the official procedure may result in non-recognition of the payment, and the student will still be considered as having outstanding dues.\\n\\nTo avoid any inconvenience, kindly:\\n\\n1. Double-check the account details before making the payment.\\n2. Keep the payment receipt/transaction reference safe and submit a copy to the accounts office or via the student portal as per standard procedure.\\n3. Do not transfer fees to any personal account or make cash payments to unauthorized individuals.\\n\\nWe appreciate your cooperation in maintaining transparency and security in all financial transactions. If you have any concerns or require assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out to your respective faculty members or the administrative office. We are always here to support you in your academic journey.\\n\\nLet me know if you'd like to make any adjustments! Thanking you.\\n\\nRegards,\\n\\nTeam Admin\\n${companyName},\\n${companyAddress},\\n${companyWebsite},\\nPhone: +91 ${companyPhone},\",\"courseSubjectTemplate\":\"Dear ${name},\\nCare Of: ${father_name},\\nMobile: ${mobile_number},\\nAddress: ${present_address},\\nCity: ${city}\\n${rollNumber}\\n\\nSubject: Confirmation of Subject List Selection - ${courseName.courseName}\\n\\nDear ${name},\\n\\nWe hope this email finds you well.\\n\\nThis email is to formally confirm the selection of your subjects in the ${courseName.courseName} Course at the time of your enrollment. The finalized list of subjects chosen by you is as follows:\\n\\n<b>Your Course Subjects are: ${subjects} </b>\\n\\nPlease note that this subject selection will remain on record for future reference and course completion requirements. In case of any changes or updates in your chosen subjects, kindly inform us in writing within [10] days from the date of this confirmation.\\n\\nWe wish you a successful and creative journey in your ${courseName.courseName} course with us.\\n\\nFor any queries, feel free to reach out at [Email/Phone].\\n\\nWarm regards,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName}\\n${companyAddress}\\n${companyWebsite}\",\"courseChangeTemplate\":\"Dear ${name},\\n\\nGreetings from ${companyName}.\\n\\nThis is to formally inform you that your request for course change has been successfully processed and changed . As per your updated enrollment, you are now registered in the newly selected course ${courseName} , and your academic records have been revised accordingly.\\n\\nWith this change, your fee structure has also been updated as per the revised course ${courseName}  curriculum and duration. The updated fee details are now reflected in our system and will be applicable from your current academic cycle.\\n\\nYou are requested to review the revised fee information shared with you and complete any pending balance (if applicable) within the stipulated time to avoid any disruption in your classes, certification, or placement assistance.\\n\\nIf you require any clarification regarding the revised course ${courseName} structure or fee breakup, feel free to contact our academic or accounts department.\\n\\nWe appreciate your continued trust in ${companyName} and look forward to supporting you in achieving your career goals.\\n\\nWarm regards,\\nCentre Manager,\\n${companyName}\\n${companyAddress}\\n${companyWebsite}\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-11T10:10:00.633Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-11T10:10:00.633Z\",\"__v\":0}]"
          },
